author: andreasmyth
msg: Moved RM persistence handler and associated retransmission queue in soap subpackage of org.objectweb.celtix.bus.ws.rm.
Added unit test coverage for methods/classes where missing.
Added public constructor to PersistenceTestServer class to prevent IllegalAccessException when security manager installed.
Added methods clearConfigurations/clearModels to ConfigurationBuidler interface.

author: cjodea
msg: Support for RESTful service implementations (no client yet)
- add support to XML binding when Provider is using Source
- allow processing of incoming messageto continue when no message is available
- infer service/port names from publish address when no wsdl is available
- put http method, path info and query string in message context
- allow endpoint to publish provider which is not using a wsdl
